   <collaboration id="sid-2d31d49d-8614-4990-8df6-a2910559f79f">
      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="It is advisable for taxpayers, especially businesses, to retain their tax records for a minimum of seven years to cover all contingencies related to audits, amendments, or future queries. By developing the data retention strategy, the Tax Relevant Transactional Data and Tax Relevant Master Data can be imported into Data models to create different primary KPIs and store them in SAP. "/>
